<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Subscription Confirmed</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2563eb;">Subscription Confirmed!</h1>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>Your subscription to the <strong>{{planName}}</strong> plan has been activated.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Business:</strong> {{businessName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Plan:</strong> {{planName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Billing:</strong> {{billingCycle}}</li>
    <li><strong>Next billing date:</strong> {{nextBillingDate}}</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
      Go to Dashboard
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>The Digital Directory Team</p>
</body>
</html>
